member.name: IObjMgr.Append
member.summary: Appends an object to the collection of managed objects.
member.param: The address of the interface of the object to be added to the list.
member.returns: Returns S_OK if successful, or a COM error code otherwise.

member.name: IObjMgr.Remove
member.summary: Removes an object from the collection of managed objects.
member.param: The address of the interface of the object to be removed from the list.
member.returns: Returns S_OK if successful, or a COM error code otherwise.

member.name: IObjMgr
member.summary: Exposes methods that allow a client to append or remove an object from a collection of objects managed by a server object.
